This repository contains code necessary to recreate analyses in: 

San Roman, A.K. et al (2022) Quantitative analysis of gene expression on the inactive human X chromosome

Each folder contains code and processed data that may be used to recreate one or more figures and tables:  
Saturation_analysis: Fig. S1
Model_fitting: Fig. S2
Linear_regressions_genes: Fig. 2, 3, S3, Tables S2, S4, S5
Linear_regressions_transcripts: Fig. S5, Table S3
Microarray_comparison: Fig. S4
Allele_specific_expression: Fig. 4, Table S6, Note S1
Gene_constraint: Fig. 5, Tables 2, S7, S8
